Comment: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這一年中央政府決定
Comment: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將人類的活動領域
Comment: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,後退到羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這之中被巨人吃掉的人數
Comment: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大約有一萬人
Comment: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,卡露拉
Comment: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我平安無事啊
Comment: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,爸爸 住手 爸爸
Comment: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你想要幹嘛?
Comment: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快點給我把手臂伸出來
Comment: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:31.52,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要！
Comment: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,爸爸因為媽媽死了就變得很奇怪
Comment: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,放開我 爸爸
Comment: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是...為了你
Comment: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在說什麼
Comment: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別忘記鑰匙
Comment: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總有一天...
Comment: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,...直到那一天
Comment: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事吧
Comment: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,做惡夢了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,感覺似乎見到了爸爸
Comment: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼可能...那是夢
Comment: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是這樣嗎...
Comment: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧
Comment: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽說有發放食物
Comment: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽說這裡是食物倉庫
Comment: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,坐船來的人通通被聚集在這裡
Comment: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這邊也是
Comment: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好好排隊
Comment: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吵死了 我可是從昨天晚上就什麼都沒吃
Comment: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們並非是真的活下來了
Comment: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你看 我趕上了
Comment: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,叔叔說這是小孩子的份 特別給我們的
Comment: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,謝謝
Comment: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他是怎樣啊
Comment: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這也是沒辦法的
Comment: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個補給應該不夠分給所有人
Comment: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣就是一天份
Comment: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難民太多了
Comment: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,況且原本食物就不足了
Comment: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你也知道住在外層的人都不被重視
Comment: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為何要為了外人用我們的補給
Comment: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,反正巨人都破壞掉城牆進來了
Comment: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果能吃掉更多人就好了
Comment: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣只會讓食物不足更嚴重
Comment: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好痛
Comment: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼...
Comment: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在做什麼 死小鬼
Comment: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明什麼都不知道
Comment: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你明明什麼都沒看過!
Comment: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人...
Comment: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是怎麼將人給...
Comment: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吵死了!
Comment: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對不起 !
Comment: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他因為肚子餓 有點火大
Comment: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以才會對大人們做這樣不禮貌的事情
Comment: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真的... 很抱歉!
Comment: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是的...
Comment: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們之所以不用挨餓
Comment: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是託我們的福啊
Comment: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是小孩 好歹也給我懷點感謝的心
Comment: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好
Comment: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可惡
Comment: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰要受那樣的人的照顧
Comment: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回去給你看 回到原來的瑪利亞之牆...
Comment: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把巨人給全部殺光
Comment: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連...
Comment: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不是認真的吧?
Comment: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是認真的!
Comment: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我跟那些在城牆裡逞強的人不同
Comment: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這種東西我才不需要!
Comment: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連...
Comment: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會餓死的喔!
Comment: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你難道不會不甘心嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是一直受到這樣的恩惠 才會打不贏巨人
Comment: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不可能啦 怎麼可能打得贏
Comment: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們只能活在城牆裡面
Comment: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亂來的話就會死
Comment: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就像我的爸媽一樣
Comment: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我們就要向他們嘻皮笑臉嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不會感到羞恥嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在... 現在也是沒辦法的啊!
Comment: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「沒辦法」什麼的 我聽膩了!
Comment: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那你就繼續這樣像個家畜一樣活著吧 膽小鬼!!
Comment: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎...
Comment: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏是膽小鬼的話...
Comment: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連跟我也是一樣
Comment: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們無論是從巨人手上逃走 還是逃離城鎮
Comment: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說到底我們什麼都沒做
Comment: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,今天的食物也是別人給的
Comment: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣沒有力量的人類...
Comment: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要打倒一隻巨人都不可能
Comment: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,最重要的是活下去
Comment: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就跟阿姨說的一樣
Comment: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎...
Comment: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我吃掉...
Comment: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好好地活下去
Comment: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不會讓艾連餓死的
Comment: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,數日後大量的難民
Comment: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了確保食物
Comment: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.65,Default,Q,0,0,0,karaoke,負責荒地的開墾
Comment: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 食物不足的災難並沒有結束
Comment: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,隔年的846年 中央政府以奪回瑪利亞之牆的名義
Comment: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將大量的難民投入於戰爭上
Comment: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總數約二十五萬人...
Comment: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,相當於人口的兩成
Comment: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但生存下來的僅100多人...
Comment: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這些犧牲讓活下來的人類的食物不足
Comment: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,逐漸獲得改善
Comment: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,全部都是巨人的錯...
Comment: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要將他們打倒
Comment: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就連我們的歸宿也能夠奪回
Comment: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏...
Comment: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我明年會志願加入訓練兵
Comment: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了得到打倒巨人的力量
Comment: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也...
Comment: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏...
Comment: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也要...
Comment: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也去
Comment: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳不去沒有關係
Comment: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳不是說最重要的是活下去嗎?
Comment: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯...
Comment: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以我是為了不讓你死而去
Comment: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我知道了...
Comment: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,三人一起...
Comment: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯...
Comment: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在起第104期訓練軍團入團儀式正式開始
Comment: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是很衰小負責帶領你們的吉斯．夏提斯
Comment: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我沒有歡迎你們的意思!
Comment: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以現在的你們來說
Comment: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只不過是給巨人當作食物的家畜
Comment: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是比家畜更卑微的存在
Comment: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對於你們這種什麼都辦不到的傢伙
Comment: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們會花三年的時間來訓練你們
Comment: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,徹底灌輸好你們打倒巨人的技術
Comment: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,三年後 你們站在巨人面前時
Comment: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只是飼料而已呢?
Comment: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還是保護國王的名譽之牆呢?
Comment: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,或是消滅巨人的光榮士兵呢?
Comment: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,由你們自己來決定吧!!
Comment: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會成為的...
Comment: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將巨人一隻不剩地趕盡殺絕
Comment: 0,0:22:25.26,0:22:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT
Comment: 0,0:24:06.70,0:24:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作為士兵失格
Comment: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發誓要對巨人復仇
Comment: 0,0:24:11.02,0:24:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,成為了訓練兵的艾連
Comment: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在基礎訓練的失敗中 所直視的真實面貌
Comment: 0,0:24:17.11,0:24:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是非常殘酷的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,title 01
