Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.20,0:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}距今100年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出現了人類的天敵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們與人類之間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有著壓倒性的力量之差
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類差點就陷入了絕種的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.97,0:00:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}倖存下來的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}建造了瑪利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.05,0:00:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}席納
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}三座城牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}實現了100年的平安生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}至始至今
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吾等貪得無厭之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}此刻如汝等所見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}此時於此地予吾等懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現食吾等生靈之罪孽制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且在這深山中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有比這更痛苦的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}放開我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊! 此外無言以對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}何等之貪欲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吾之罪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在此該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}此等罪孽還之我身...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明差一點就能救到媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要給我多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.16,0:04:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}差一點點..就能將媽媽...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:18.22,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我適可而止點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你之所以沒有辦法救出你媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為你沒有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我之所以沒辦法面對巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是因為我沒有勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}啊...又變成這樣了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點 往裡面疏散
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}用停靠在那邊的船逃離希干希納
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點 不然要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}位於城牆外側
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟希干希納區一樣突出的地區
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}做為吸引巨人的誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}達成了降低警備成本與兵力的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如同它的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.98,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}做為巨人們的目標的希干希納居民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只好從唯一的一個後門逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全部人都給我把行李丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能多讓一個人上去也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是艾連跟米卡莎還沒...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在先別說話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看那個樣子想必...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在磨蹭些什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}砲彈怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}神明大人..神明大人..神明大人..神明大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.60,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5} 已經客滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出航了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼這樣 拜託讓我上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}即使只有小孩子也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}很抱歉 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}出航
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓我上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓我上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}混帳 在瞄準哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是這東西沒有瞄準器可以瞄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在那種事情隨便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點裝填下一枚砲彈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.83,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}門要關了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}撤退 要被關在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別關門 再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還有很多人留在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果這扇門被突破的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這可不是一座城市被占據就能了事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類的活動區域 將被迫退到下一座城牆後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算如此也沒有理由對自己眼前的人見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點關起來 巨人要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點關門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}開火!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來了 撤退!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}衝過來了 快點將門...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}門被...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}瑪利亞之牆南部希干希納區淪陷數小時後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這件事情傳遍了人類領域內的各個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是真的嗎? 希干希納被巨人入侵了這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}撐了100年的城牆為何現在...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論你相不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在可是真的有坐船逃出的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}依照報告有500人左右
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}問題是只有希干希納而已嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是 應該不可能侵入到瑪利亞之牆的內陸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總之先通知中央 等待指示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.81,0:12:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種緊急狀況 光憑我們無法作出對策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.06,0:12:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就在剛剛快馬來報 瑪利亞之牆被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.19,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}內陸被巨人入侵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.13,0:12:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類又要被巨人吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結束...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經無法...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回到那個家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到最後我還在跟她做無謂的鬥嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}媽媽已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}哪裡都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:12:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼會這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為...你沒有力量...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.52,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是我..因為人類太弱小了?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難道弱者就只能哭泣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把他們...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從這世界上...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了嗎? 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}徹底地殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從這世上...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一隻不留地...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這一年中央政府決定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將人類的活動領域
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.74,0:13:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}後退到羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這之中被巨人吃掉的人數
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大約有一萬人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我平安無事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸 住手 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你想要幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快點給我把手臂伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:31.52,Upside,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}爸爸因為媽媽死了就變得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.39,0:14:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}放開我 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是...為了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別忘記鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.27,0:14:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總有一天...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}...直到那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}做惡夢了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.77,0:15:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}感覺似乎見到了爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼可能...那是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是這樣嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽說有發放食物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}聽說這裡是食物倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}坐船來的人通通被聚集在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好好排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.66,0:15:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吵死了 我可是從昨天晚上就什麼都沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們並非是真的活下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你看 我趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}叔叔說這是小孩子的份 特別給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他是怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個補給應該不夠分給所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣就是一天份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}難民太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且原本食物就不足了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你也知道住在外層的人都不被重視
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為何要為了外人用我們的補給
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反正巨人都破壞掉城牆進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果能吃掉更多人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣只會讓食物不足更嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在做什麼 死小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你明明什麼都沒看過!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是怎麼將人給...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對不起 !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他因為肚子餓 有點火大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.96,0:17:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以才會對大人們做這樣不禮貌的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真的... 很抱歉!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們之所以不用挨餓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可是託我們的福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算是小孩 好歹也給我懷點感謝的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}誰要受那樣的人的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.51,0:17:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}回去給你看 回到原來的瑪利亞之牆...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}把巨人給全部殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.99,0:17:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不是認真的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是認真的!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我跟那些在城牆裡逞強的人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這種東西我才不需要!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.29,0:18:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會餓死的喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你難道不會不甘心嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就是一直受到這樣的恩惠 才會打不贏巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不可能啦 怎麼可能打得贏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們只能活在城牆裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}亂來的話就會死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.56,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就像我的爸媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以我們就要向他們嘻皮笑臉嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不會感到羞恥嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在... 現在也是沒辦法的啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「沒辦法」什麼的 我聽膩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.55,0:18:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那你就繼續這樣像個家畜一樣活著吧 膽小鬼!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏是膽小鬼的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連跟我也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們無論是從巨人手上逃走 還是逃離城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}說到底我們什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}今天的食物也是別人給的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.13,0:19:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這樣沒有力量的人類...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}要打倒一隻巨人都不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}最重要的是活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就跟阿姨說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我吃掉...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好好地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不會讓艾連餓死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}數日後大量的難民
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了確保食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.65,Default,Q,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}負責荒地的開墾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.51,0:19:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是 食物不足的災難並沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}隔年的846年 中央政府以奪回瑪利亞之牆的名義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.10,0:19:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將大量的難民投入於戰爭上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}總數約二十五萬人...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}相當於人口的兩成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但生存下來的僅100多人...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這些犧牲讓活下來的人類的食物不足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}逐漸獲得改善
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.57,0:20:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}全部都是巨人的錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要將他們打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就連我們的歸宿也能夠奪回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我明年會志願加入訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為了得到打倒巨人的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.20,0:21:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.51,0:21:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也要...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.83,0:21:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳不去沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳不是說最重要的是活下去嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所以我是為了不讓你死而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我知道了...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}三人一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.24,0:21:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在起第104期訓練軍團入團儀式正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我是很衰小負責帶領你們的吉斯．夏提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我沒有歡迎你們的意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以現在的你們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只不過是給巨人當作食物的家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.00,0:21:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是比家畜更卑微的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.28,0:21:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對於你們這種什麼都辦不到的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們會花三年的時間來訓練你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}徹底灌輸好你們打倒巨人的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}三年後 你們站在巨人面前時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只是飼料而已呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}還是保護國王的名譽之牆呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}或是消滅巨人的光榮士兵呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}由你們自己來決定吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.90,0:22:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我會成為的...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將巨人一隻不剩地趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.70,0:24:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作為士兵失格
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.09,0:24:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}發誓要對巨人復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.02,0:24:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}成為了訓練兵的艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.60,0:24:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在基礎訓練的失敗中 所直視的真實面貌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.11,0:24:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是非常殘酷的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.82,0:24:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}
